abstract: David Letterman has edged ahead of his long-time rival Jay Leno in several important viewer categories as the new television season concludes its third week.
snippet: David Letterman has edged ahead of his long-time rival Jay Leno in several important viewer categories as the new television season concludes its third week.
lead_paragraph: It may not be cause for celebration, because his audiences continue to decline, but David Letterman has edged ahead of his long-time rival, Jay Leno, in several important viewer categories as the new television season concludes its third week.

headline.main: Letterman Tops Leno Among Younger Viewers
